FBIS4-13998 "drnes080_r_94011" FBIS-NES-94-080 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 India Punjab Akali Dal-Badal Suspends Political Activities Punjab Akali Dal-Badal Suspends Political Activities BK2204160394 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 22 Apr 94 BK2204160394 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] The five-member presidium of the Akali Dal-Badal in Punjab has announced suspension of the party's political activities for an indefinite period. Addressing a news conference at Jullundur today, the members of the presidium said that under the existing circumstances, it is not possible to carry on the political activities of the party. As already reported, the party president, Mr. Prakash Singh Badal, resigned yesterday and set up the five-member presidium to run the party's affairs.
